<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2128] Further parallelizaton of ParallelMultiSearcher</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2128</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When calling &lt;tt&gt;search(Query, Filter, int)&lt;/tt&gt; on a ParallelMultiSearcher, the &lt;tt&gt;createWeights&lt;/tt&gt; function of MultiSearcher is called, and sequentially calls &lt;tt&gt;docFreqs()&lt;/tt&gt; on every sub-searcher. This can take a significant amount of time when there are lots of remote sub-searchers.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
